{"tid":1090652,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本南北行程求意見","createTime":"2019-04-03T15:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T10:03:30.000Z","uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15baf2c72d54e1de22e58e3791e393aac94fa6e7","tid":1090652,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:19:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 我7月就飛去日本, plan左個行程<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅位置即係未confirm, 想大家俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要都係剩低以下幾日未搞掂, 當然其他日子有提議都歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\nDay 2: 想問下波照間島值唔值得去? 因為船飛來回都7千yen, 住宿又未book到<br />\n如果即日來回就真係叫去左日本最南到此一遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDay 17 &amp; 18: 想問下大家會選擇搭巴士定搭jr呢? 價錢計落差唔多<br />\n<br />\n行程如下:<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n香港飛石垣<br />\n14:00  - 17:50 定期観光バスＢコース（石垣島半周観光 + 玻璃船): <a href=\"http://www.azumabus.co.jp/sightseeing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.azumabus.co.jp%2Fsightseeing%2F&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=35bf085c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.azumabus.co.jp/sightseeing/</a><br />\n出海觀星船<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ishigaki-diving.net/cruise_tingahra.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ishigaki-diving.net%2Fcruise_tingahra.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=5747531b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ishigaki-diving.net/cruise_tingahra.html</a><br />\n<br />\n石垣食店:<br />\n辺銀食堂<br />\n八重山そば処 来夏世(Kunatsuyu) (八重山麵)<br />\nNative DELi (牛扒)<br />\nＣＯＲＮＥＲ&rsquo;Ｓ・ＧＲＩＬＬ(石垣牛漢堡扒) <br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />波照間島: (日本最南端之碑)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />酒店觀星團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10:00 船返石垣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlunch後行去石垣島鍾乳洞<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n飛去東京羽田<br />\n買東京廣域PASS&gt; 水戶<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n水戶 偕樂園, 国営ひたち海浜公園, 日立站<br />\n<br />\nDay 6<br />\n袋田瀑布 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.town.daigo.ibaraki.jp/page/page001474.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.town.daigo.ibaraki.jp%2Fpage%2Fpage001474.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=3518c849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.town.daigo.ibaraki.jp/page/page001474.html</a><br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\n東京<br />\nHomemade Ramen 麦苗<br />\n成蔵  (3月閉店, 4月重開, 再睇tabelog)/ 麺屋一燈<br />\n<br />\nDay 8<br />\n東京羽田飛去稚內<br />\n食: 車屋 源氏/ 竹ちゃん<br />\n<br />\nDay 9<br />\n稚內觀光 (宗谷岬, 宗谷丘陵, 防波堤)<br />\n宗谷岬(可買來回飛, 2500yen): <a href=\"http://www.soyabus.co.jp/routebus/souyacape\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.soyabus.co.jp%2Froutebus%2Fsouyacape&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=cd5f2461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.soyabus.co.jp/routebus/souyacape</a><br />\ndinner: 海鮮炉端 うろこ亭/ 車屋 源氏<br />\n<br />\nDay 10<br />\n去禮文(06:20～08:15) (行桃岩) (落雨就join 8:35 禮文A巴士團)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.soyabus.co.jp/teikan/course\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.soyabus.co.jp%2Fteikan%2Fcourse&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=8e8ad226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.soyabus.co.jp/teikan/course</a><br />\n<br />\nDay 11<br />\n禮文行山(禮文林道, 約3小時)<br />\n<br />\nDay 12<br />\n禮文去利尻 (13:25～14:10) &gt; 14:25 巴士團-B (14:25発 &rarr; 17:05着)<br />\ndinner たにかわ庵<br />\n<br />\nDay 13<br />\n利尻&gt; 姫沼展望台&gt; 食堂 丸善<br />\n利尻飛返札幌新千歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買北海道7day pass(24000yen) (如果join巴士團, 唔買pass)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間可以去機場3樓食芝士<br />\n機場&gt;帶廣<br />\n<br />\nDay 14<br />\n幸福, 愛國站<br />\n豬扒飯<br />\n<br />\nDay 15<br />\n馬場, 白樺通, 甜品<br />\n<br />\nDay 16<br />\n帶廣&gt; 札幌市內<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Day 17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n札幌&gt; 旭川&gt; ラベンダー畑駅(富山農場)&gt; 美馬牛(四季彩之丘)&gt; 美瑛(拼布之路)(睇時間)&gt; 札幌<br />\nOR<br />\n巴士團 &quot;L-2&quot;/ &quot;N&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://teikan.chuo-bus.co.jp/tw/cms/course\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fteikan.chuo-bus.co.jp%2Ftw%2Fcms%2Fcourse&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=ba03875b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://teikan.chuo-bus.co.jp/tw/cms/course</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Day 18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n札幌&gt; 余市蒸餾所&gt; 柿崎商店 海鮮工房&gt; 札幌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nikka.com/distilleries/yoichi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nikka.com%2Fdistilleries%2Fyoichi%2F&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=aa7b9295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nikka.com/distilleries/yoichi/</a><br />\nOR<br />\n巴士團 &quot;K&quot;<br />\n<br />\nDay 19<br />\n札幌 (新千歲機場) &gt; 東京 (成田國際機場)<br />\n東京 (成田國際機場)  &gt; 香港 (香港國際機場)"},{"pid":"33fcf6fcaa6207e134ddd47d3746a10e6997736b","tid":1090652,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"Fail啦<br />\n最南應該去沖之鳥島<br />\n最北應該去北方四島"},{"pid":"82b711f9ec6cd8984dbbd79d3fa8db8266df0b9a","tid":1090652,"uid":186681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"Day 13<br />\n利尻&gt; 姫沼展望台&gt; 食堂 丸善<br />\n利尻飛返札幌新千歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買北海道7day pass(24000yen) (如果join巴士團, 唔買pass)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間可以去機場3樓食芝士<br />\n機場&gt;帶廣<br />\n<br />\n你不如去附近洞爺支勿住一住先 好趕一定唔得"},{"pid":"15878d16ed3d59bb0a3261d4aa38e72b85f31838","tid":1090652,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82b711f9ec6cd8984dbbd79d3fa8db8266df0b9a","tid":1090652,"uid":186681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"Day 13<br />\n利尻&gt; 姫沼展望台&gt; 食堂 丸善<br />\n利尻飛返札幌新千歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買北海道7day pass(24000yen) (如果join巴士團, 唔買pass)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間可以去機場3樓食芝士<br />\n機場&gt;帶廣<br />\n<br />\n你不如去附近洞爺支勿住一住先 好趕一定唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"飛機時間係14:20 - 15:15<br />\n然後4點半先係機場走, 應該唔趕喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jwYnWz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jwYnWz.png&h=84563499&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}